@startuml Sequence_File_Management

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "File API" as API
participant "Validator" as Validator
participant "Cloudinary" as Cloud
participant "Database" as DB

== Upload File ==
User -> Client: Select file
Client -> Client: Read file
Client -> Validator: Validate file type
Validator --> Client: Type valid
Client -> Validator: Validate file size
Validator --> Client: Size valid
Client -> API: POST /api/files/upload
API -> Validator: Validate file
Validator --> API: File valid
API -> Cloud: Upload file
Cloud -> Cloud: Process file
Cloud --> API: File URL
API -> DB: Save file metadata
DB --> API: File saved
API --> Client: Return file URL
Client --> User: Display uploaded file

== Image Optimization ==
User -> Client: Upload image
Client -> API: POST /api/files/upload-image
API -> Cloud: Upload image
Cloud -> Cloud: Optimize image
Cloud -> Cloud: Generate thumbnails
Cloud --> API: Image URLs
API -> DB: Save image data
DB --> API: Image saved
API --> Client: Return URLs
Client --> User: Display optimized image

== Video Processing ==
User -> Client: Upload video
Client -> API: POST /api/files/upload-video
API -> Cloud: Upload video
Cloud -> Cloud: Process video
Cloud -> Cloud: Generate streaming URL
Cloud --> API: Video URLs
API -> DB: Save video data
DB --> API: Video saved
API --> Client: Return URLs
Client --> User: Display video player

@enduml

